         <div type="translation" source="#mehier1904" xml:lang="fr">
         <p>M. Nasif et M. Mathlich, fils fidèles, ont élevé ce monument à leur mère Mnimir? très chérie</p></div>
         <div type="translation" resp="#jmr" xml:lang="en">
            <p>Of M(archius) Nasif and M(archia) Mathlich, mother; the Marchii Nimira and Fydel, their sons, had this built for their dear parents.</p></div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>A photograph taken by flashlight by Mr. Michael Ballance in <date>1955</date> has made possible a more accurate reading of the text.</p>
